    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822170/extras/Banner1.png?t=1638547296\" /></span><br>Gardenia: Prologue is a free, standalone version of Gardenia. The story takes place on a different island, but you will notice some connections to the main plot of  Gardenia.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822170/extras/Garden1.gif?t=1638547296\" /></span><br>You’ll have a chance to try your gardening and crafting skills, rearrange the vegetation of the island, build roads and fences.  Remember to take photos of your beautiful garden compositions! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822170/extras/Banner2.png?t=1638547296\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822170/extras/Garden2.gif?t=1638547296\" /></span><br>The storyline is focused on the character of a both gentelman and a genius inventor Mr. C. Sum, who is researching some artifacts on the island and has certain tasks for the player.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822170/extras/Banner4.png?t=1638547296\" /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822170/extras/Garden4.gif?t=1638547296\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>An atmosphere of relaxation on a distant paradise island</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Arrange the space the way you want to create beautiful plant compositions</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A beautiful story to experience and a mystery to unravel</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A unique crafting system based on the Magic Crafting Table</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dexterity elements (magic mushrooms and their properties)</li></ul>",
